### Backend API base URL
@backendUrl = http://localhost:8080
@jsonServerUrl = http://localhost:5000

### =====================================================
### Backend Master Data API (Primary)
### =====================================================

### Get all cities
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/public/master-data/cities
Accept: application/json

### Get all job fields
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/public/master-data/fields
Accept: application/json

### Get all skills
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/public/master-data/skills
Accept: application/json

### Get all specializations
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/public/master-data/specializations
Accept: application/json

### =====================================================
### JSON Server (Fallback/Legacy)
### =====================================================

### Get all IT job categories and roles
GET {{jsonServerUrl}}/it_jobs
Accept: application/json

### Get one IT job group by id
GET {{jsonServerUrl}}/it_jobs/1
Accept: application/json

### Get all job fields from JSON server
GET {{jsonServerUrl}}/job_fields
Accept: application/json

### Get skills from JSON server (if exists)
GET {{jsonServerUrl}}/skills
Accept: application/json

